<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>NorthCraft | New Lead</title>

<style>

/* CSS WILL BE ADDED IN THE NEXT STEP */

</style>

</head>

<body>

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">

<tr>

<td align="center">

<table class="email-container" role="presentation" width="700" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">

<!-- ====================================================== -->
<!-- HERO -->
<!-- ====================================================== -->

<tr>

<td class="hero">

<div class="brand-tag">

NEW LEAD NOTIFICATION

</div>

<div class="monogram">

NC

</div>

<h1>

NORTHCRAFT

</h1>

<p class="tagline">

Curated • Thoughtful • Memorable

</p>

<div class="gold-divider"></div>

<h2>

🎁 A New Premium Enquiry Has Arrived

</h2>

<p class="hero-text">

A potential customer has shown interest in NorthCraft's premium gifting experience.

Review the details below and connect with the customer at the earliest opportunity.

</p>

</td>

</tr>

<!-- ====================================================== -->
<!-- CUSTOMER DETAILS -->
<!-- ====================================================== -->

<tr>

<td class="section">

<h3>

Customer Information

</h3>

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">

<tr>

<td class="info-card">

<div class="label">

FULL NAME

</div>

<div class="value">

<%= name %>

</div>

</td>

</tr>

<tr>

<td height="18"></td>

</tr>

<tr>

<td class="info-card">

<div class="label">

EMAIL ADDRESS

</div>

<div class="value">

<%= email %>

</div>

</td>

</tr>

<tr>

<td height="18"></td>

</tr>

<tr>

<td class="info-card">

<div class="label">

PHONE NUMBER

</div>

<div class="value">

<%= phone %>

</div>

</td>

</tr>

</table>

</td>

</tr>

<!-- ====================================================== -->
<!-- MESSAGE -->
<!-- ====================================================== -->

<tr>

<td class="section">

<h3>

Customer Requirements

</h3>

<div class="message-card">

<div class="quote-mark">

"

</div>

<p>

<%= message %>

</p>

</div>

</td>

</tr>

<!-- ====================================================== -->
<!-- REMINDER -->
<!-- ====================================================== -->

<tr>

<td class="reminder">

<h3>

✨ Recommended Action

</h3>

<p>

Respond within the next <strong>30–60 minutes</strong>.

Fast responses significantly increase the chances of converting this enquiry into a successful corporate gifting opportunity.

</p>

</td>

</tr>

<!-- ====================================================== -->
<!-- FOOTER -->
<!-- ====================================================== -->

<tr>

<td class="footer">

<div class="footer-logo">

NC

</div>

<h2>

NORTHCRAFT

</h2>

<p>

Premium Corporate Gifting

</p>

<p>

Luxury Hampers • Festive Collections • Employee Welcome Kits

</p>

<div class="footer-divider"></div>

<p class="footer-tagline">

Curated • Thoughtful • Memorable

</p>

<div class="footer-badge">

Premium Lead Notification

</div>

</td>

</tr>

</table>

</td>

</tr>

</table>

</body>

</html>
